roomplan.nvim is an original MIT-licensed implementation.

The project interoperates with the Norg file format documented by the
nvim-neorg/norg-specs project. Neorg itself is GPL-3.0 licensed; no Neorg
implementation code is copied into this repository.

venn.nvim (MIT) informed the research into terminal line-junction rendering.
The RoomPlan renderer is independently implemented and contains no copied
venn.nvim source at this time.
